headline: 3 Dividend Growth Stocks That Can Deliver a Lifetime of Passive Income
summary: The allure of high-yield dividend stocks often tempts income investors.  With its compelling valuation, established dividend track record, and strong brand presence, Target offers investors a rare combination of current income and growth potential.
